protected_spaces_details.description: Provision for children and young people

description: Demolition of garages adjacent to Bronte House and erection of two single to seven-storey blocks to provide 133 dwellings (comprising flats & maisonettes, including 75 affordable units) with associated landscaping and amenity space on roundabout adjoining Kilburn Park Road and Carlton Vale, NW6, including removal of pedestrian footbridge and stopping-up of western side of existing roundabout and subject to a Deed of Agreement under Section 106 of the Town and Country Planning Act 1990, as amended
